snippet: General Manager Mike Tannenbaum remains positive that the Jets — despite injuries and a 2-2 start — will play like the Super Bowl team he envisioned.
abstract: New York Jets general manager Mike Tannenbaum maintains that the Jets, despite injuries and a 2-2 start, are a championship team.
